message.content: Yes, the bus set out from Dinas. So much is established. Ifor Hw Evans, Propr, watched it go from the windows of the Dinas Motor Omnibus Co. Very interested, Ifor was. For there was his garage hand, Dai, Pugh, taking a doleful farewell of Morfydd Owen, Morfydd, who had until recently been Ifor's typist, but was now returning to her home town as a fully-fledged schoolteacher.
